68
00:07:37,309 --> 00:07:39,892
(bell chiming)

69
00:07:42,991 --> 00:07:43,824
Claudia.

70
00:07:44,807 --> 00:07:45,890
Si Signora.

71
00:07:49,727 --> 00:07:51,800
