260
00:24:23,154 --> 00:24:24,237
Ma Signora.

261
00:24:25,166 --> 00:24:26,416
[Naomi] Come.

262
00:24:38,720 --> 00:24:40,841
I'm Kimi Evans, my
associates and I have been

263
00:24:40,841 --> 00:24:45,225
